            . On the day stated, the prisoner came and took a pair of boots off the door of the prosecutor's shop - I pursued him, and never lost sight of him till he was taken - these are the boots.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am quite innocent; I did not take them - a man gave them to me to hold.</p>
